  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Through long and intensive training you mastered Alchemical Crafting. Few people in this world can match your capabilities in this area.</p><p>Gain the following master feats: @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.fOIUmDGa9gkeCHA0]{Supertaster}.</p><p><strong>Skill Potency</strong></p><p>At 9th level, you gain a +2 item bonus to Crafting checks involving @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.rmwa3OyhTZ2i2AHl]{Craft}. At 17th level, if you have @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.v62QzTwHOT3t86cL]{Craft Anything}, @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.VRCBTEyrcBf7auGz]{Legendary Tattoo Artist}, this bonus increases to +3.</p>",
